[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":266},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F13\u002Fgulp-series-17-conclusion\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F13\u002Fgulp-series-17-conclusion\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F13\u002Fgulp-series-17-conclusion\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F13\u002Fgulp-series-17-conclusion\u002F":244,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F13\u002Fgulp-series-17-conclusion\u002F":251},"\u002Fgulp\u002F20190613\u002F3304187145\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":225,"date":226,"description":227,"extension":228,"lang":229,"meta":230,"navigation":231,"path":232,"readingMinutes":233,"seo":234,"standalone":235,"stem":236,"tags":237,"tldr":241,"updated":241,"url":242,"__hash__":243},"content\u002Fen\u002FGulp\u002Fgulp-series-17-conclusion.md","Gulp Series: Wrapping Up","7145330418",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":214},"minimark",[11,16,20,24,31,39,42,45,48,58,64,68,74,79,84,184,188,197,200],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"End of the series — kind of. It's a wrap-up, but also a beginning, because there's still plenty I haven't covered. I might write some bonus chapters later when I have time.",[12,21,23],{"id":22},"wrap-up","Wrap-up",[17,25,26],{},[27,28],"img",{"alt":29,"src":30},"From the web","https:\u002F\u002Flc-gold-cdn.xitu.io\u002F525072a07f737c146231.png",[17,32,33,34,38],{},"Took a few days to reorganize the Gulp stuff I hadn't touched in two months into this ",[35,36,37],"strong",{},"Gulp Series: It's Not a Drink, It's a Task Runner",". I originally thought I'd write about 10 posts to cover Gulp, but the momentum kept going — from basic Gulp all the way to GitHub deployment.",[17,40,41],{},"This is just one phase of the Gulp series — I haven't covered things like jest tests yet. Future posts will be bonus chapters since not everyone uses unit testing, pug, ejs, etc.",[17,43,44],{},"Revisiting Gulp also gave me a clearer sense of how it differs from Webpack. Honestly I really like Gulp's API docs — copy-paste with light tweaks usually just works.",[17,46,47],{},"Future post links will be added here but not pushed to the GitHub repo.",[17,49,50,51],{},"Sample repo: ",[52,53,57],"a",{"href":54,"rel":55},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002FgulpSample",[56],"nofollow","GitHub Repo",[17,59,60,61],{},"See you in the bonus chapters ",[62,63],"d",{},[12,65,67],{"id":66},"full-gulp-series-index","Full Gulp Series Index",[69,70,71],"blockquote",{},[17,72,73],{},"If you're new, don't skip around — go in order, otherwise you might get lost.",[75,76,78],"h3",{"id":77},"main-chapters","Main chapters",[69,80,81],{},[17,82,83],{},"Recommended order:",[85,86,87,94,100,106,112,118,124,130,136,142,148,154,160,166,172,178],"ul",{},[88,89,90],"li",{},[52,91,93],{"href":92},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F09\u002Fgulp-series-01-intro\u002F","Gulp Series: Intro",[88,95,96],{},[52,97,99],{"href":98},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-02-install\u002F","Gulp Series: Installing Gulp",[88,101,102],{},[52,103,105],{"href":104},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-03-basics\u002F","Gulp Series: Basic Gulp",[88,107,108],{},[52,109,111],{"href":110},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-04-scss\u002F","Gulp Series: Installing SCSS",[88,113,114],{},[52,115,117],{"href":116},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-05-postcss\u002F","Gulp Series: Installing PostCSS",[88,119,120],{},[52,121,123],{"href":122},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-06-css-minify\u002F","Gulp Series: Minifying and Optimizing CSS",[88,125,126],{},[52,127,129],{"href":128},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-07-simplify\u002F","Gulp Series: Simplifying the Gulp Flow",[88,131,132],{},[52,133,135],{"href":134